#: ../../H/has-the-X-nature.rst:5
msgid "has the X nature"
msgstr "has the X nature"

#: ../../H/has-the-X-nature.rst:7
msgid ""
"[seems to derive from Zen Buddhist koans of the form \"Does an X have the "
"Buddha-nature?\"] adj. Common hacker construction for ‘is an X’, used for "
"humorous emphasis. \"Anyone who can't even use a program with on-screen help"
" embedded in it truly has the :ref:`loser` nature!\" See also :ref:`the-X-"
"that-can-be-Y-is-not-the-true-X`\\. See also :ref:`mu`\\."
msgstr ""
"[「XはBuddha-natureを持っているか?」という形式の禅仏教の公案に由来すると思われる]形容詞 ‘is an "
"X’を表す一般的なハッカー的構文で、滑稽な強調のために使われる。「画面に埋め込まれたヘルプ付きのプログラムさえ使えない者は、真に\\ "
":ref:`loser`\\ の本性を持っている!」。\\ :ref:`the-X-that-can-be-Y-is-not-the-true-X`\\"
" も参照。\\ :ref:`mu`\\ も参照。"
